<geoCoordinate id="8CCC72A1FFDFFFBBFF2BFBB9FEC5FBCB" box="[151,292,1034,1060]" degrees="126" direction="east" minutes="52.1" orientation="longitude" pageId="15" pageNumber="100" precision="92" value="126.86833">126º52.1'E</geoCoordinate>
). Confirmed specimens have been collected from the Ryukyu Islands only, but underwater photographs show that the species is widely distributed in tropical regions of the western pacific.
</paragraph>
